Airbnb Pricing Analysis in Berlin

Junqian Zhang

Introduction

  • Detect how different variables influence the Airbnb Price in Berlin
  • Provide a model for price prediction by linear regression and decision tree

Data Description

  • Price as dependent variable
  • 7 independent variables
